Jung San (Korean: 정산; born (1985-01-23)January 23, 1985), more commonly known by his stage name San E (Korean: 산이), is a South Korean rapper.
He debuted in 2010 under JYP Entertainment, where he was the label's first solo rapper.
He left the company in 2013 to sign with hip hop label Brand New Music.
He left the company in 2018 and established hip hop label FameUs
Entertainment in 2019.
